dataSource.query:
SELECT
	 event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
    "Time until man. orders delivered (days)",
    "Time until SO items with GI posted (days)",
    "Man. orders delivered after scheduled finish date (%)",
    "Man. orders with underdelivery (%)",
    "Man. orders with zero prod. time in material master (%)",
    "GI posted after planned GI date in SO item (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Manufacturing orders delivered") 
        	AS "Time until man. orders delivered (days)",
        AVG ("4 - Lead time from start - Sales order items with goods issue posted") 
        	AS "Time until SO items with GI posted (days)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Manufacturing orders delivered after scheduled finish date") * 100 
        	AS "Man. orders delivered after scheduled finish date (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Manufacturing orders with underdelivery") * 100 
        	AS "Man. orders with underdelivery (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Manufacturing orders with zero in-house production time in material master") * 100 
        	AS "Man. orders with zero prod. time in material master (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Goods issue posted after planned goods issue date in sales order item") * 100
        	AS "GI posted after planned GI date in SO item (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
    GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
